<div id="pitch">
	<div class="bind">

		<div class="gift"></div>

		<dl>
			<dt class="simple" title="Simple"><span>Simple</span></dt>
			<dd>No accounts, no signups, no fees.  Just a <strong>better way</strong> to plan your gift.</dd>

			<dt class="fast" title="Fast"><span>Fasy</span></dt>
			<dd>Starting tracking your gift contributions <strong>quickly</strong>&hellip; in fewer than two minutes!</dd>

			<dt class="easy" title="Easy"><span>Easy</span></dt>
			<dd>No complex forms to navigate.<br />Just the bare <strong>essentials</strong> to start planning.</dd>
